sops.sop:
Workflow:
1. User -> Transportation Planner;
2. Transportation Planner -> Accommodation Planner 
   Transportation Planner -> Restaurant Planner 
   Transportation -> Attractions Planner (in parallel);
3. Accommodation Planner, Restaurant Planner, Attractions Planner -> Plan Checker;
4. Plan Checker -> Final Plan Summarizer;
5. Final Plan Summarizer -> End.

Description:
First, the Transportation Planner selects 3 distinct Texas cities and establishes a transportation framework (flights/driving) between Daytona Beach and Texas locations within the budget. This framework guides parallel planning for Accommodation, Restaurants, and Attractions. The Plan Checker validates budget compliance and logistical coherence across all components, ensuring total costs remain under $3,600. Finally, the Summarizer compiles a detailed itinerary optimized for solo travelers.
